Class GeometryBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.gpe.prov.gml.parser.v2.geometries.GeometryBinding

    public class GeometryBinding
extends Object
    This class parses a geometry. It is also used to get the attributes for a GML geometry.
